{"tid":1177881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑人夫婦湖邊野餐 白人老太太持槍驅趕","createTime":"2019-05-30T04:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T06:37:56.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"488d7b563c198b9197a8a9362098354810fc83ed","tid":1177881,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vyTcubE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvyTcubE.png&h=f22c8864&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n（北美通訊）美國密西西比州一對非裔夫婦周日外出郊遊，帶著愛犬到湖邊野餐，豈料遭一名穿著營地服務公司制服的白人老太太持槍驅趕。事實上，民眾到湖邊休憩區根本不需要預約，營地服務公司發聲明表示，已經開除這名濫用槍械的管理員。<br />\n<br />\n記者：林宜萱<br />\n<br />\n李察臣（Jessica Richardson）周日和退伍軍人、現職獸醫的丈夫，去到斯塔克維爾（Starkville）一處湖泊邊野餐。這座湖鄰近美國連鎖營地服務公司Kampgrounds of America（下稱KOA）據點。兩人到達湖邊不到五分鐘，一名駕駛農夫車的白人老太太對他們大吼，更帶著槍械下車。<br />\n<br />\n這名身穿KOA職員制服的老太太指，他們沒有預約，必須離開。李察臣向她表示，不知道湖邊需要預約，但若他們夫婦違反規定，可以好好溝通，沒必要拔槍。<br />\n<br />\n李察臣夫婦離開後，途經營地管理辦公室，想向一名經理反映剛才的狀況，發現這名經理是那位老太太的丈夫，兩人都是營地管理員。老太太的丈夫說，湖邊野餐不用預約。而KOA周二表示，公司不容許濫用槍械，已經開除這名老太太。"},{"pid":"ddc9fdf6ee83f58b9610209b82334623275e171c","tid":1177881,"uid":11034,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:48:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vynkC5O.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvynkC5O.gif&h=40a0fc1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78fd51f0df96db0da0d2aaf2235c7bfaec7cf3fe","tid":1177881,"uid":4258,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:49:16.000Z","msg":"老公都唔撐佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28163f184f7074233e71c2aea2f95208bfbed40e","tid":1177881,"uid":197337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"78fd51f0df96db0da0d2aaf2235c7bfaec7cf3fe","tid":1177881,"uid":4258,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:49:16.000Z","msg":"老公都唔撐佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:52:50.000Z","msg":"老公都係受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b8a8f53fa2cf2dd4eb26ca76e668a79fb40e13","tid":1177881,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:54:44.000Z","msg":"密西西比州 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDeep South 到你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8ce475fec784b091960dc97fe474a53bc829e6","tid":1177881,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:54:49.000Z","msg":"cls好慘"},{"pid":"982c935d75a80021623ecd58daa219531940e289","tid":1177881,"uid":193893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:57:54.000Z","msg":"呀婆vs黑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑人又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86650e12057873c9d0780bc3b8d7accb7b462a5e","tid":1177881,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28163f184f7074233e71c2aea2f95208bfbed40e","tid":1177881,"uid":197337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"78fd51f0df96db0da0d2aaf2235c7bfaec7cf3fe","tid":1177881,"uid":4258,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:49:16.000Z","msg":"老公都唔撐佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:52:50.000Z","msg":"老公都係受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T04:58:59.000Z","msg":"黑暗兵法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8f32412fae98f881ca6db838d7ac4c420c6f39","tid":1177881,"uid":16034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T05:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兇錯